      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a solid choice for someone needing reliable transportation on a budget. While the engine and transmission are in good working order and have been serviced regularly, the car does show its age. You will find several noticeable scratches and minor dents on the exterior, and the interior upholstery has some visible wear and staining from years of use. It is a dependable daily driver that prioritizes function over aesthetics.",
